      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="20168763">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/puppygo/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4086279-15.jpg" alt="扒皮狗" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20168763/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20168763/" class="">明天还要继续</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/puppygo/" class=" " title="扒皮狗">扒皮狗</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="20168763">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">我终于发现，随着年纪的增长，人的胆量却在逐渐下降，这种胆怯来自越来越多的顾忌和牵挂。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-08-06 13:06</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">2人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                我终于发现，随着年纪的增长，人的胆量却在逐渐下降，这种胆怯来自越来越多的顾忌和牵挂。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

